http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/10-village-accountants-suspended/article13997386.ece

Ten village accountants in Chintamani taluk of Chickballapur district have been suspended on charges of misappropriation of funds.Chickballapur Deputy Commissioner M.V. Venkateshamurthy issued orders on Wednesday in this connection. The village accountants have been accused of swindling funds released for drought relief works in 2014-15.Assistant Commissioner Amaresh issued notices to 18 village accountants on charges of misappropriation of funds last year. Ten among them were suspended as the charges were proved prima facie and departmental enquiry was initiated against eight others, sources said.